annotationMIRIAM

public static void annotationMIRIAM(uk.ac.ebi.miriam.db.MiriamLocalProvider linkMiriam,
                                    String URI,
                                    Hashtable<String,String> table,
                                    String type)
Method to fill the Maps used in the program using MIRIAM WS.
Provide it the Miriam link object create in the constructor.
Put the URI official and the SBGN correspondance.
For the molecule mapping, this method will be correspond all the URI of a database with the correspondance in SBGN format
exemple: 
 annotationMIRIAM(linkMiriam, "http://www.bind.ca/", annotationSpecies, "simple chemical");
 
 fill the molecule mapping Map with:
 
 annotationSpecies{key: "http://www.bind.ca/", "simple chemical"}
 annotationSpecies{key: all the URLs for BIND, "simple chemical"}

Parameters:
linkMiriam - Object MIRIAM to link the Web service
URI - URI, address official of the database
table - Map to fill
type - value in the MAP
